Eat Pray Love;;2010;;PG-13;;Biography,Drama,Romance;;5.8;;Ryan Murphy;;Julia Roberts,Javier Bardem,Richard Jenkins,Viola Davis,I. Gusti Ayu Puspawati,Hadi Subiyanto,Billy Crudup,A. Jay Radcliff,Mike O'Malley,Ashlie Atkinson,James Franco,Lisa Roberts Gillan,Ryan O'Nan,Gita Reddy,Dwayne Clark,Jen Kwok,Mary Testa,Elijah Tucker;;Liz Gilbert (Roberts) had everything a modern woman is supposed to dream of having - a husband, a house, a successful career - yet like so many others, she found herself lost, confused, and searching for what she really wanted in life. Newly divorced and at a crossroads, Gilbert steps out of her comfort zone, risking everything to change her life, embarking on a journey around the world that becomes a quest for self-discovery. In her travels, she discovers the true pleasure of nourishment by eating in Italy; the power of prayer in India, and, finally and unexpectedly, the inner peace and balance of true love in Bali.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0879870/